<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='847003' id='t-847003'>&quot;unless.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='849371' id='t-849371'>But the &quot;unless&quot; word is also attached</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='853828' id='t-853828'>to that other, most terrifying phrase,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='858804' id='t-858804'>&quot;If only I had ...&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861463' id='t-861463'>&quot;If only I had ...&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='864191' id='t-864191'>If you ever have that thought
ricocheting in your brain,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='869461' id='t-869461'>it will hurt a lot.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='873007' id='t-873007'>So, those are the many reasons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='875659' id='t-875659'>why you are going to fail</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='877659' id='t-877659'>to have a great career.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='881198' id='t-881198'>Unless --</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='886698' id='t-886698'>Unless.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='889912' id='t-889912'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
